name: Space Capybara vs Cyber Cat (demo)
description:
Space Capybara vs Cyber Cat 

Capybara captain: Oh no, that evil cyber cat and his minions are back again. Capybara pilot: We must assembly a squadron to destroy them. 
Capybara captain: Do it, do it, do it now!
Capybara pilot: Space Capybaras, lets take them down.
Capybara captain: What are those evil cyber cat lasers?!

Space Capybara vs Cyber Cats is a physics based endless runner where you control a group of Space Capybaras ships while dodging obstacles and fighting the evil Cyber Cats for the highest score.
